</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-04-02-0121-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-04-02-0121-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>Capt. John Lamb and his independent company of New York artillerymen were captured in the abortive attack on Quebec, 31 Dec. 1775.</p>

